{"tid":2276520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度總理莫迪恭賀擁有當地血統的賀錦麗當選！","createTime":"2020-11-08T01:36:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T03:20:42.000Z","uid":91914,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a7671fe3ef7d269710a1a37f83dfa803b680e68a","tid":2276520,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T01:36:54.000Z","msg":"死印狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出賣侵侵<br />\n<br />\n印度總理莫迪（Narendra Modi）恭賀擁有當地血統的賀錦麗，形容這場選舉是「一個新的里程碑」。<br />\n<br />\n02:02：法國總統馬克龍（Emmanuel Macron）、德國總理默克爾（Angela Merkel）、西班牙首相（Pedro Sanchez）桑切斯分別恭賀拜登和賀錦麗。<br />\n<br />\n01:50：英國首相約翰遜（Boris Johnson）及加拿大總理杜魯多（Justin Trudeau）分別祝賀拜登勝選。約翰遜表示美國是英國最重要的盟友，並期望在共同優先問題上與拜登緊密合作。"},{"pid":"0ad42cf4d0af97caa4cccd584be32b0ef806982b","tid":2276520,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T01:38:06.000Z","msg":"賀錦鯉"},{"pid":"d201460c7e46544d0406bb6625a0a856d9975c07","tid":2276520,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T01:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e9cf43c682cff82951356230035e2af9c19c92","tid":2276520,"uid":242831,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T01:38:12.000Z","msg":"外交禮儀姐"},{"pid":"8952701ff43104dd5249e647909538eb6e643b8b","tid":2276520,"uid":171192,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T01:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/2481421256ae9d93df7e72b90a421564/tenor.gif?itemid=18080376\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F2481421256ae9d93df7e72b90a421564%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D18080376&h=f5583bff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3b3958aeb522c87331b4745921d789c3fd6260f","tid":2276520,